description: React/TSX component patterns for card-max project
globs: src/components/**/*.tsx
alwaysApply: false
---

# Component Patterns

- Named exports only: `export function ComponentName`
- Props interface above component: `interface Props { ... }`
- Add `data-testid` on root element for testing
- Import types from `../../specs/data/offer.schema` (single source of truth)
- Use `BANK_METADATA` for bank colors and display names
- Conditional classes via array `.join(" ")` — no classnames library

# Client Components

- Mark with `"use client"` at top of file
- Use `useRouter`, `useSearchParams`, `usePathname` from `next/navigation`
- Wrap in `<Suspense>` in parent when using `useSearchParams`

# Offer Card Conventions

- Bank color bar at top using `style={{ backgroundColor: bankMeta.color }}`
- Merchant logo fallback: colored initial avatar
- Expiry badges: red for expired, orange for expires-soon
- Category as pill badge in footer
- Entire card is an `<a>` linking to `sourceUrl` with `target="_blank"`
